data.description: This 7.3 Acers of paradise surrounded on 3 sides by the Williams Fork River, has a guest campsite w/firepit & beach area to enjoy the river. Endless nights of stars gazing & seasonal river play, brown trout in river. Updated kitchen featuring Granite Counters, Stainless steel appliances, hardwood floors, Pantry, fresh interior paint, well water (4 wells on site) 2 additional power taps on the property, irrigation system, Main level wood burning fireplace, basement wood burning stove, water filter system, cistern system town water hauled in or well water available, Barn & chicken coop, Shed used as guest Cabin/Camp & firepit, Livestock okay, walkout basement, mud room, yard and garden area, large cement slab ideal for courtyard or basketball, frequently visited by wild life such as Deer & Elk, close to Craig and the national forest. Needs some TLC like carpet, bathroom flooring and to have furnace serviced, Breathtaking views all around you! Close to outdoor activities, hiking, fishing, & hunting. Primary Residence, seasonal use, nightly rental. Sold AS IS!
